<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١١ - <span class="c2">(٢٢٦٧)</span> وَقَالَ: فَقَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3745">أَبُو سَلَمَةَ </a>، قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1219">أَبُو قَتَادَةَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">« مَنْ رَآنِي فَقَدْ رَأَى الْحَقَّ .»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>